articles.title: Australia braces for most powerful cyclone in 8 years - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Ilsa reached the highest Category 5 intensity Thursday over the Indian Ocean and is expected to maintain that destructive level as it crosses the Pilbara coast. | World News
